Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.00,0:01:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#03幸运猴子挥汗如雨挖洞烧烤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.54,0:01:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馆内已经发现敌人放置的爆炸物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.05,0:01:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有人员请尽速前往防爆室避难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.28,0:01:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,距离自爆装置启动前还有5分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.49,0:01:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶，光是对付外面的敌人就已经够麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.66,0:01:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次是特洛伊木马吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.44,0:01:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特特洛伊，特特洛伊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.66,0:01:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们还无法解除啊真是笨手笨脚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.16,0:02:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个臭炸弹在说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.27,0:02:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花，冷静一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.77,0:02:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是为了让我们迷惑焦虑而故意装置的简单陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.14,0:02:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可以中计呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.61,0:02:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猪头，猪头，猪头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酒精，酒精，酒精
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.00,0:02:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果只是想互淋啤酒应该不需要打火机吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.35,0:02:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.06,0:02:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.09,0:02:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.09,0:02:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是零食店的签
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.73,0:02:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这玩意绝对不是那么好玩的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.50,0:02:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.17,0:02:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顺著这些管道前进的方块
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.60,0:02:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碰到最下面的引爆装置大概就会爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.37,0:02:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该错不了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.14,0:02:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然这样挡下那些方块不就行了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.61,0:02:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情没有那么简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.65,0:02:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方块上面有个节拍计时器不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.22,0:02:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.92,0:02:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这叫钟摆引信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.92,0:02:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果随便去动它让它碰到旁边的金属的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.52,0:02:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.69,0:03:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个混蛋炸弹我要宰了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.56,0:03:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，我不是说过了这只是简单的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开卡车撞上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.60,0:03:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是危险又美丽啊，香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶，太麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.67,0:03:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用这个强力胶把所有方块的计时器黏起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.48,0:03:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让它们停下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.18,0:03:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.11,0:03:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黏著计时器的方块全都是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.75,0:03:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,万一某个被挡住而导致炸弹爆炸的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.29,0:03:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那该怎么办才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只剩5分钟而已耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.46,0:03:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，距离自爆装置启动只剩1分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.39,0:03:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么!你的4分钟、3分钟2分钟都跑哪去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.30,0:03:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是少女的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.67,0:03:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶，欺人太甚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.57,0:03:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，不可以啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花，不要阻止我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.07,0:03:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你扔过去的话炸弹会．．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.21,0:03:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那该怎么办才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.27,0:03:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，你想怎么做呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.41,0:03:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个形状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.62,0:03:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，时间快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.41,0:03:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了，你滚一边去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.78,0:03:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没办法了那我们先去防爆室吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.75,0:04:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，我忘了说一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.29,0:04:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦我爆炸的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.39,0:04:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,半径两公里之内的东西都会蒸发掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.13,0:04:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.66,0:04:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.03,0:04:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个该不会是．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该不可能吧．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.37,0:04:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多要开始了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.24,0:04:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是说不定．．．说不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.47,0:04:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞬间移动，瞬间移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快要爆炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.71,0:04:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快要爆炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.63,0:04:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞬间移动，瞬间移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.65,0:04:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停下来．．．了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.71,0:04:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.69,0:04:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么停下来的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.66,0:04:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竹轮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竹轮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.53,0:04:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是我们和竹轮的邂逅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.60,0:04:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了，梅尔优他们呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.77,0:04:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，敌人逐渐消灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.47,0:04:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞬间移动，瞬间移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，不得了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.24,0:04:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前些时候的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.31,0:05:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被各位打得落花流水的敌国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.95,0:05:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然派了一群人来向我们道谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.28,0:05:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，好不容易战争就要结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.65,0:05:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么一来你们最喜欢的那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.06,0:05:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.93,0:05:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，”那个”是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.46,0:05:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个嘛，那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.60,0:05:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.20,0:05:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说的”这个那个”到底是什么啦中校!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧，他还有脉搏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.64,0:05:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，进行人工呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.61,0:05:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘴对嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.60,0:05:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘴对嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.28,0:05:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们干嘛跑开?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.55,0:05:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这还用问吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.08,0:05:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家会嫁不出去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.12,0:05:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别闹了这关系到一条人命耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.19,0:05:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你帮他做不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.09,0:05:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是伤脑筋想想别的办法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.03,0:05:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也不想帮他做人工呼吸吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.99,0:05:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，因为这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.00,0:05:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拯救中校的新方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，有什么办法吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你问我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.27,0:05:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，例如拿葱卷在他的脖子上?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果要说这个的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.21,0:06:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放颗酸梅在额头上，如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.21,0:06:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该是把沙丁鱼头放在额头上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後加以膜拜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.66,0:06:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蛋酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.25,0:06:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，这是治疗感冒的方法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.72,0:06:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，那其它呢?还有没有什么办法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.49,0:06:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白饭不要咬，直接吞下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.03,0:06:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惊吓他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.96,0:06:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在手上写一个”人”字然後吞10次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.33,0:06:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，香草，大家都很认真在想办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.67,0:06:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在吃什么竹轮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.67,0:06:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊，你干嘛吃竹轮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.24,0:06:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竹轮?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.31,0:06:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中间是空的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.94,0:06:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来吧，梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.78,0:06:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样就不会碰到嘴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.41,0:06:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空气也通得过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.55,0:06:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很安全喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.92,0:06:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.12,0:06:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以各位，等打倒眼前的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.70,0:06:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡过这次的危机之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有各位最喜欢的这个和那个还有那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.04,0:07:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全都免费赠送一年份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.52,0:07:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这样，我们成功完成任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.15,0:07:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迎接战争结束的到来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.69,0:07:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等协约签订後战争就结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.76,0:07:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.56,0:07:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶不过，我还是无法接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.53,0:07:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发给终结战争英雄的礼物居然是一年份的竹轮?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.61,0:07:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我们一年份的竹轮，到底要我们怎么用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.04,0:07:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有用啊，可以拿来当作竹轮型印章盒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.21,0:07:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，你拿的那个不就是签订停战协约的印章吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.35,0:07:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，对喔！我忘了把印章拿给提督
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.52,0:08:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这下惨了，据说对方是最重视礼仪的战斗部族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.63,0:08:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记带印章来的事万一被发现的话．．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.06,0:08:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又要开战了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.18,0:08:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我拿印章去给提督
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.17,0:08:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.10,0:08:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛阻止我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我当然要阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.14,0:08:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对方可是很重视礼仪的部族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.71,0:08:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算要拿印章过去也不能被发现啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.58,0:08:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是要怎么拿过去呢?在这样众目睽睽之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.68,0:08:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.79,0:08:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要把它吹过去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞砸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.63,0:08:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在搞什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.06,0:08:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竹轮不是拿来这样用的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.46,0:08:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.51,0:08:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这种情况下使用竹轮的确是有点困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.27,0:08:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,双方对於协约的内容已经确认同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.91,0:08:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来进行签名盖章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.71,0:08:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这下完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.11,0:08:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昙花一现的和平啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.45,0:08:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.95,0:09:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竹轮?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.38,0:09:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.06,0:09:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提督想用竹轮代替印章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，这个主意棒透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.69,0:09:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶，竹轮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来总算顺利完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.15,0:09:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.98,0:09:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这都是竹轮的功劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.42,0:09:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.59,0:09:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吹这个笛子的意思是把大家都杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.03,0:09:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(外星语)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.13,0:09:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，他在生气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.76,0:09:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来这个世界没那么好混，光靠竹轮就想解决所有的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.54,0:09:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.24,0:09:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心电感应，心电感应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.14,0:09:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(其实是我把印章搞丢了)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.68,0:10:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(这一切都是我的错，对不起．．．)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.51,0:10:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(什么!你这个笨蛋插花女!)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.68,0:10:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算诚实去道歉也没用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,简直是火上加油嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.32,0:10:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该说是刚才那个画面有很多地方能让人吐槽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.20,0:10:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘻呼哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.03,0:10:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘻呼哈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.14,0:10:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘻呼哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.14,0:10:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘻呼哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.90,0:10:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘻呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.91,0:10:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘻呼哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.91,0:10:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.75,0:10:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.12,0:10:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么关系呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.02,0:10:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这样，多亏有竹轮才得以顺利签订和平条约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.99,0:10:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我们也变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.93,0:10:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有竹轮，什么都办得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.13,0:10:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有竹轮任何逆境都能克服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.73,0:10:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这样我们跟竹轮成了不可分离的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.15,0:11:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们是天使队吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.55,0:11:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉，请你们消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们已经玩完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.95,0:11:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就很难说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.42,0:11:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.22,0:11:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是无敌的天使队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.46,0:11:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为现在的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.39,0:11:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.03,0:11:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.12,0:11:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.60,0:11:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个?那个是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.40,0:11:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼，你想知道吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.30,0:11:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是创造了无数奇迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.21,0:11:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拯救我们脱离无数危机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.94,0:11:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这个竹轮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.37,0:11:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，那是竹轮麸啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.41,0:11:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,动手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.00,0:11:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竹轮永远不灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.12,0:11:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猜拳十三奥义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.52,0:11:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始罗，剪刀石头布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.40,0:11:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被媒体发现热恋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.16,0:11:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被媒体发现热恋是天大的绋闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剪刀和石头也感到动摇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.16,0:11:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是对於布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.03,0:12:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,问题是这个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.93,0:12:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,表面上看起来像是个迷糊蛋大好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.20,0:12:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实这种类型最危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.51,0:12:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.67,0:12:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底在打什么算盘?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.24,0:12:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有，没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊，那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.58,0:12:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.42,0:12:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.29,0:12:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做了蛋糕要不要一起来吃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊?蛋糕?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.49,0:12:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#04友情鱼肉片试吃价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.50,0:12:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草莓奶油蛋糕?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.03,0:12:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊，我特地做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.30,0:12:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是天使队的人都出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.91,0:12:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使队成员的梅尔优居然请我吃蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.51,0:12:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一定是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.32,0:12:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对有什么阴谋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.48,0:12:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，那里有一只蝴蝶在飞耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.03,0:12:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.69,0:12:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毒药反应，无
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.02,0:12:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火药及爆炸物反应，无
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.23,0:13:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,细菌和生化武器的痕迹也找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.16,0:13:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.49,0:13:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千岁，那是什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道耶 可能是牛肉罐头吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.61,0:13:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，请喝茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.37,0:13:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.94,0:13:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是这杯红茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.01,0:13:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这杯茶里一定有剧毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.75,0:13:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.62,0:13:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，快点吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.05,0:13:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会被她杀死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.99,0:13:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，张开嘴巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.39,0:13:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸，妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.69,0:13:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请原谅我的不孝比你们先走一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.79,0:13:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千岁这十七年来一直体弱多病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.53,0:13:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本没有做过一件好事．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.30,0:13:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,味道怎么样?千岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.71,0:13:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.97,0:13:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了，你喜欢吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.91,0:13:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，还有很多喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.04,0:13:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为大家的份我都做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.99,0:13:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千岁，这些全都要吃完喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.32,0:13:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千岁，这些全都要吃完喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.35,0:14:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，有一种幸福的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.39,0:14:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是耍这种招数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.73,0:14:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好难受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.30,0:14:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然相信天使队的笨蛋成员我实在太傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.00,0:14:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，那个蛋糕真的好好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.64,0:14:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说不定那个梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.41,0:14:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以成为我真正的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.28,0:14:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话虽这么说但她毕竟是天使队的成员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.05,0:14:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能那么轻易就相信她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.56,0:14:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有没有什么办法可以确认梅尔优是不是真的想跟我做朋友?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.20,0:14:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要开始罗，梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.50,0:14:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猪肉切片，猪肉切片，我爱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.17,0:14:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，突然头晕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.14,0:14:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千岁，危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.08,0:15:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，梅尔优居然奋不顾身的冲出来救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.11,0:15:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我居然怀疑她，实在是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.45,0:15:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨死了，笨死了，笨死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.52,0:15:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.06,0:15:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到会在那里撞上电车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.36,0:15:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再也不相信任何人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.93,0:15:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了，我记得她说今天要做起司蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.60,0:15:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，她怎么可能故意把我扔去给电车撞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.74,0:15:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，为了以防万一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.25,0:15:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千岁，振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.38,0:15:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是答应我要跟我一起吃起司蛋糕吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不可以死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她已经往生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.16,0:15:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像我这种生病专家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.24,0:15:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让心脏停个几秒钟根本就是小事一桩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.71,0:16:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她在哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.17,0:16:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的死，你真的很伤心啊梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.58,0:16:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在你的心里原来这么有份量啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.15,0:16:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我居然那样恶毒地测试你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.96,0:16:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见了，千岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.69,0:16:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶，你怎么死掉了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.26,0:16:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易进来了一个好女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.63,0:16:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样我真的会死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.73,0:16:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超魔术，挣脱大成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千岁，原来你还活著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.27,0:16:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，你按的是什么东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.08,0:16:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，不要按啊为什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.04,0:16:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(一个月後)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我．．．我还以为我死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.02,0:16:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然把我活生生的射出宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.39,0:16:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这下你的狐狸尾巴终於露出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.46,0:16:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优·樱叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.79,0:16:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.79,0:16:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要一起来吃苹果派啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.73,0:17:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,苹果派的花语是友情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.19,0:17:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优难道你真的把我当好朋友?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.34,0:17:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.94,0:17:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你搞什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.04,0:17:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.44,0:17:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你自己撞过来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.28,0:17:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底出了什么事?千岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.75,0:17:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么打扮成这个样子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.15,0:17:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗哩罗嗦的吵死了快点向我道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.15,0:17:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要我向你道歉可是究竟要道什么歉呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.99,0:17:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪，听得见声音却看不见人影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.73,0:17:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔，因为你太矮了所以我没看见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.53,0:17:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，还有那边的老太婆妆画的还真浓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.27,0:17:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说我是老太婆?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.94,0:17:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.14,0:17:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，梅尔优，救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.61,0:17:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到天使队的人在欺负我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.41,0:17:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优一定会出面救我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.92,0:17:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.25,0:17:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?为什么香草会在这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.09,0:17:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.22,0:17:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优出去买东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.76,0:18:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,震惊．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.20,0:18:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次不论发生什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.50,0:18:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我绝对不再相信梅尔优·樱叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?千岁吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.22,0:18:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊，那家伙一边找大家麻烦一边在找你耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟她之间发生了什么事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.01,0:18:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有，什么都没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.25,0:18:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说不定千岁是希望梅尔优能陪她玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.65,0:18:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.42,0:18:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的很笨耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.99,0:18:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是她想跟你做朋友啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.72,0:18:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟千岁本来就是朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.79,0:18:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.53,0:18:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千岁，你是怎么了?怎么这样一身狼狈呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.70,0:18:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，因为发生了一些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.07,0:18:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了，我刚才做了泡芙等一下要不要一起吃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.27,0:18:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对错不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.24,0:18:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优是曾出现在我梦中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.45,0:18:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.77,0:19:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，好美喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.64,0:19:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能跟真正的朋友起这样开心的逛庙会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.05,0:19:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我连想都没想过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.35,0:19:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在正在享受有生以来第一次的幸福滋味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.42,0:19:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.09,0:19:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，我总觉得好像少了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.63,0:19:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对对，就是这种感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.13,0:19:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在不是高兴的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.20,0:19:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，快点逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.04,0:19:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危险，梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.01,0:19:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千岁，你不要紧吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.08,0:19:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这点小伤算不了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.71,0:20:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来吧，梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.01,0:20:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用我们两人友情的威力来歼灭敌人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.22,0:20:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用我们两人友情的威力来歼灭敌人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，请看这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.39,0:20:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是新型的扩散能源炮现在是试用期间大优惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.36,0:20:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,装在梅尔优的机体土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.23,0:20:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然外形好像没什么变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.59,0:20:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，那我就赶快来试用看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.13,0:20:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.60,0:20:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.61,0:20:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.07,0:20:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪?千岁呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.14,0:20:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(三个月後)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.25,0:20:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的名字叫乌丸千岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.48,0:20:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也为了追求真正的友情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.02,0:20:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迷失於战场的可怜女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.59,0:20:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.11,0:20:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我找了你好久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.96,0:20:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅．．．梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.20,0:20:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，跟我一起回去托朗斯巴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.77,0:20:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能跟你回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.00,0:21:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.58,0:21:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要跟你在一起我就会很不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.18,0:21:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千岁，把自己的不幸怪罪到别人身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.65,0:21:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样不太好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.34,0:21:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是铁证如山的事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.92,0:21:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么这么说我们不是好朋友吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.99,0:21:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好朋友?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.22,0:21:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错吧，千岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.06,0:21:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.00,0:21:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个人．．．你这个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.17,0:21:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.59,0:21:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你终於醒啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.95,0:21:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你们救了我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.65,0:21:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是，是梅尔优把你救出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.12,0:21:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊，然後三天三夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.65,0:21:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她几乎没有睡觉都在病床边照顾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.09,0:21:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.66,0:21:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了，你终於醒来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.96,0:21:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想说你也差不多要醒了所以特地做了这个东西来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.43,0:22:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，刚出炉的巧克力蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.57,0:22:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要，我不要朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.67,0:22:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请好好补充营养喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.71,0:22:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
